Hi Raffaella,

I hope you're doing well. My apologies resending with correct spelling of y=
our name.

I am just touching base with you with regards to the electronic items that =
you took with you from the property (laptops, tablets, and mobile phones) t=
hat you have concerns about.

I can arrange for our assessment company, Connect, to carry out an assessme=
nt of these items for you. They will provide the necessary packaging so you=
 can send the items directly to them.

All I need is a list of said items and I can get that arranged for you.

Kindest Regards


Sasha C
